    <p>Over 100 species of birds have been sighted at the farm. The old site's bird photos live in a <a href="https://photos.google.com/share/AF1QipPBzHETbG_HIKlpJG55OtCBanE_lGzFn4kzB8guZ7OCVRxVjqMcWvSEV9NXusiSPw" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">shared Google Photos album</a> — but the best way to explore what's actually been seen (birds included) is our live biodiversity explorer.</p>
    <a class="button" href="/biodiversity">Explore live sightings →</a>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--tint">
